{"tid":1420943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"純和理非 想搞個辯論會有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:34:48.000Z","uid":230798,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe32f47b6758605e74ce94043a341d156f7c6a3","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"「代post」<br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅我想搞個係屋邨或民居附近搞辯論會，成分係100%分理嘅。 <br />\n喺Facebook演算法底下，藍絲只會睇到佢哋個族群嘅資訊，喺網上對話只會係鬥屌收場，我認為面對面更能容易動之以情訴之以理，所以希望搞啲新嘢，只要大家覺得有搞嘅價值，就應該試下。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知大家有冇啲藍嘅屋企人，我認為佢哋唔係惡只係未明白，我希望令佢哋明白。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">亦覺得如果大家都能夠做多少少</span>，咁可能成功就大一分，死嘅傷嘅拉嘅就少一個。<br />\n<br />\n我明好多藍唔講道理，但我願意去試，用佢哋嘅方式去試。對話唔能夠解決所有嘅問題，但如果可以我相信大家都會用對話解決。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果參加嘅，我需要可以係比人打以外都可以冷靜，講嘢有條理嘅巴絲，記住唔可以互屌，一屌我哋就會比佢哋貼labe。</span><br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n1) 令藍吸收第二邊嘅資訊<br />\n2) 從媒體上曝光我哋願意主動同不同意見人仕溝通<br />\n3) 吸收佢哋嘅立場話唔定對我哋有幫助<br />\n<br />\n執行方式：(Draft)<br />\n1) 於<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屋邨或民居附近</span>擺設街站<br />\n2) 邀請藍絲與我方進行辯論，1分鐘為一節，每方均有3節發言機會<br />\n3) 辯論結束主動邀請對方握手<br />\n<br />\n需要文資：(Draft)<br />\n1）辯論所用枱櫈<br />\n2）Facebook Live器材(手機，腳架，Facebook Page)<br />\n3）事件懶人包傳單/backdrop之類<br />\n<br />\n參與人仕：(Draft)<br />\n1）辯論者3 - 5名(不同年齡階層，學生，青年，中年，銀髮)<br />\n2）派傳單3 - 5名(派比花生友)<br />\n3）保安5名（有乜事藍打人都可以有人幫拖）<br />\n<br />\n我都希望大家可以傾下有冇嘢改善"},{"pid":"1f8931bf2e55a571b1a7f00b4483f7e5e039a3f5","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"0933ad9a4885b01b0c0c8e6d72e64a3fd82bdd5d","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"35c828c05f86b59189c31b3d0586fdf13910ee72","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"2e7b85ec992e982c71ae863aae8a554a33493a5f","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"eb229dcd840f0fd3b849c5f6072bfbaebd131972","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"25c96101bd042417df9c7a092d8232da6bf41792","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"cd38f0b242cf93fb17c6738bd2382ff5c669131c","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:40.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"1eef4f9959c914e4c476cfab32d64f795d6ea0ec","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"86392336f0546069d40a64f9d45f2b880a17813e","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"477b542d349ce9a8c174b575da0f7df7a5cffe7d","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4a33a35a9aa6a3842c1ed976e25e75c59c470b7b","tid":1420943,"uid":140297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"等睇藍絲笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa308fda5870e0c84c22ce2739aa7b7d105f978","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NLgJNxFFujX0wMiQ6xLGpw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNLgJNxFFujX0wMiQ6xLGpw&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=c5a7590f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NLgJNxFFujX0wMiQ6xLGpw</a><br />\n大家想一齊搞嘅可以入tg gp傾"},{"pid":"e095525a45a01adff5dd88e45394ad5c106209eb","tid":1420943,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:29:11.000Z","msg":"應該搞洗腦會"},{"pid":"1a4b404f9332b04179966401bfc1b50b3e8be9a6","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb5fc946ba7c2d71c086f5160a95ccf0f08a1905","tid":1420943,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"純個人諗法<br />\n<br />\n感覺唔太有用，<br />\n不過都好多謝巴打嘅提議<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n因為如果目標係藍至深藍<br />\n其實佢地已經唔會太思考<br />\n（或者調轉，會獨立思考 + 廣泛信息，應該唔會仲停響深藍 或 藍）<br />\n辯論會佢會先入為主覺得你講嘅野都錯<br />\n未必有用<br />\n<br />\n其實可以諗諗反其道而行<br />\n搞個深藍分享會<br />\n等淺藍同中立嘅<br />\n了解下深藍嘅人係點諗（包括對 警察濫權、包庇黑社會、政府大白象工程 同殖蝗主義）<br />\n<br />\n反而可以令到佢地反省返自己<br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該棄深藍 救淺藍"},{"pid":"d95f57a986421a67338f75a6881c4e24fac4411b","tid":1420943,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"邀請藍絲同場辨論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf2261a5d0079feb6e9439ce33daf93ca5c196b","tid":1420943,"uid":290258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94e1c686a64e82d39d834b466c6cb6cf2426f346","tid":1420943,"uid":290258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0093cf71a0ea71cbeed6c1ca625fd5f3a8c792c5","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ecb2d0437a0b3b7d459f149854341b7713e8a02","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb5fc946ba7c2d71c086f5160a95ccf0f08a1905","tid":1420943,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"純個人諗法<br />\n<br />\n感覺唔太有用，<br />\n不過都好多謝巴打嘅提議<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n因為如果目標係藍至深藍<br />\n其實佢地已經唔會太思考<br />\n（或者調轉，會獨立思考 + 廣泛信息，應該唔會仲停響深藍 或 藍）<br />\n辯論會佢會先入為主覺得你講嘅野都錯<br />\n未必有用<br />\n<br />\n其實可以諗諗反其道而行<br />\n搞個深藍分享會<br />\n等淺藍同中立嘅<br />\n了解下深藍嘅人係點諗（包括對 警察濫權、包庇黑社會、政府大白象工程 同殖蝗主義）<br />\n<br />\n反而可以令到佢地反省返自己<br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該棄深藍 救淺藍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"多謝您意見，應該咁講我都target嘅係啲應為阻民生影響搵食嗰堆人，唔係冇得救嗰堆。嗰堆人唔係唔講道理只係唔聽年青人講，所以我會插入銀髮族幫忙。"},{"pid":"2f89324e6441445e0d2ae18de560078105381220","tid":1420943,"uid":230798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d84d5aa024e82f55411d83e343dba9f0d567b42","tid":1420943,"uid":225933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"認為阻住生活既吾一定係藍絲 好多都係純粹吾希望阻到佢地生計 養一頭家真吾易<br />\n佢地吾一定撐警 也有可能希望年輕人做到野 所以我覺得我地要佢地既支持既同時 都要為下佢地著想 人地所做既都只係為頭家"},{"pid":"1a80ff6387913b2bd3b880e9f9fcba12f7d6439d","tid":1420943,"uid":14171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:53:53.000Z","msg":"我怕到時變咗天下第一武鬥大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676be152e2765071ca2d496c1b5b4ca698ca0282","tid":1420943,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"因為除左佔領機場渣政府春袋以外，<br />\n成場運動和理非 / 勇武缺一不可，<br />\n而黎個方法係可以改變和理非勇武分化局面，<br />\n對勇武黎講係尤其重要！！<br />\n<br />\n8月6號做到第一次，大家壯到膽，淋病 <br />\n每日跨部門記招/ 黑狗記招政府 既洗腦分化陰招<br />\n已經可以破解，<br />\n我地挽留和理非甚至提升我地既民意支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原理係：<br />\n<br />\n1）當港共約時間安排記招，<br />\n2）馬上吹雞搵d 講野OK/議論能力比較強既手足外（最少10個以上，和理非勇武需合作無間） <br />\n+/- 一兩個立法會議員/組織代表去記招出面睇live（如果可以），<br />\n3）完左後挽留班記者朋友，善用時機，馬上開民間記招。<br />\n<br />\n禁既話，<br />\n最重要既效果係<br />\n- 政府無辦法控制資訊唱衰我地，一面倒講我地做到有幾衰（除某紅媒），從而抗分化、抗洗腦。<br />\n- 民間記者會可以用黎交待香港黑警 點樣 濫權濫暴 投訴無門。同時，可以搵受傷既街坊/ 被濫暴既對象去交待/反駁返政府會上既大話，為整場運動增加說服力<br />\n- 文宣不是和理非既專利，近日發生左好多事，我明白各手足都好嬲，但勇武既行為係紅媒/藍絲渲染之下開始被部分和理非/淺黃（部分為三毛所扮演）割蓆，黎個係鐵一般既事實。催淚彈入民居，係可以令部分街坊勇武，但不停破壞狗屋/BBQ 係會令和理非/淺黃 對勇武卻步。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民間記招，勇武係可以向市民講清楚自己既底線，同時可以進行公民再教育/ 輸出革命。</span></span></strong>所以民間記者會，勇武既參與係為整場運動落定心丸！！勇武一定要黎！！！！（完記招後既行動我無建議）<br />\n- 請善用記招既號召力。當你係地鐵站禁辛苦先airdrop 到一張圖出去，或者留係同溫層分享資訊，或者你同旁邊食飯嘅藍絲阿伯理論。只要黎個民間記招講一兩三句，聽到既人講緊既係幾百萬人，係包埋 鍾意聽收音機成日屌7你既司機，同鍾意睇cctvb既廢老藍絲啊！！民間記招可以宣傳將來行動/方向，又唔洗被瘋狂藍絲費老搞到爆血管，仲可以黎支持君亞bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同各大媒體記者手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，性價比同佔領機場睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n- 我地都可以做好形象大使，（例如：手足來自各行各業，上黎講會令運動增加民意授權 / 我地身無屎，唔會似班狗官調頭走避問題，禮貌加分）<br />\n<br />\n有人擔心時間準備不足，講完一定有好多位被人，<br />\n開記招講錯野分分鐘仲大獲，不如另約時間在開記招。<br />\n<br />\n但我強調點解一定要馬上開民間記招，有以下兩個優點，<br />\n第一，唔洗另約傳媒同地點。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n第二（好重要），媒體播新聞次序係跟單新聞既重要性/時間性，</strong></span></span><br />\n港共記招後民間記招，新聞次序就好大機會港共記招接住落民間記招，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>個效果就好似係辯論比賽，你屌我馬上博，</strong></span></span><br />\n禁就唔會令對家偷換概念，合理化我地做既所有野。<br />\n再者，佢依家五大訴求一個都無應承，你淨係Jer住佢黎個point，<br />\nelab下再講行動點動搖到政府，其實真係唔洗好勁議論能力都講到<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n講著緊多先，我已經兩日無訓，但堅持打埋落去，<br />\n第一係因為我覺得work，<br />\n同時，我唔想個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>400個義士做condom</strong></span></span>，<br />\n要對得起佢地，<br />\n就係唔好令整個革命付之流水。<br />\n<br />\n大家比下意見啦，我訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不分化，不割蓆</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n林病月娥 屌你老母"}]}